languages.text: "Смотрю на вас, а страх не берет. Наверно, я столько аварий повидал, что смерти уже не боюсь".
"You know, I look at you, but I'm not scared at all. I guess I've seen too many disasters to be afraid of death."

languages.text: «Por más que te miro, no tengo miedo, curiosamente. Será que he visto demasiados desastres como para tenerle miedo a la muerte».
languages.original_text: "You know, I look at you, but I'm not scared at all. I guess I've seen too many disasters to be afraid of death."

traits.locale_text: «Por más que te miro, no tengo miedo, curiosamente. Será que he visto demasiados desastres como para tenerle miedo a la muerte».

languages.text: 「あなたを見ていても、全く怖くないんです。絶望を見てきたからこそ死が怖くないんでしょうね」
languages.original_text: "You know, I look at you, but I'm not scared at all. I guess I've seen too many disasters to be afraid of death."

traits.locale_text: 「あなたを見ていても、全く怖くないんです。絶望を見てきたからこそ死が怖くないんでしょうね」

languages.text: “说真的，虽然你就站在我面前，但我心里一点都不怕。大概是因为我见识过太多灾难，死亡已经吓不倒我了。”
languages.original_text: "You know, I look at you, but I'm not scared at all. I guess I've seen too many disasters to be afraid of death."

traits.locale_text: “说真的，虽然你就站在我面前，但我心里一点都不怕。大概是因为我见识过太多灾难，死亡已经吓不倒我了。”

languages.text: "Wisst Ihr, ich sehe Euch an, habe aber keine Angst vor Euch. Ich habe wohl schon zu viele Katastrophen erlebt, um den Tod zu fürchten."
languages.original_text: "You know, I look at you, but I'm not scared at all. I guess I've seen too many disasters to be afraid of death."

traits.locale_text: "Wisst Ihr, ich sehe Euch an, habe aber keine Angst vor Euch. Ich habe wohl schon zu viele Katastrophen erlebt, um den Tod zu fürchten."

languages.text: « Vous savez, quand je vous regarde, je n'ai pas peur du tout. Il faut croire que j'ai vu trop de désastres au cours de ma vie pour craindre la mort. »

languages.text: "Ne var, biliyor musun? Sana baktığımda korkmuyorum bile. Sanırım ölümden korkamayacak kadar çok felakete şahit oldum."
